de.espirit.firstspirit.client.plugin.report

  • Packages that use de.espirit.firstspirit.client.plugin.report 
    Package Description
    de.espirit.firstspirit.client.plugin
    Provides interfaces and types for client plugins.

    This package provides types, interfaces and classes, that are to be used to integrate client plugins via the public hotspot of FirstSpirit.
    de.espirit.firstspirit.client.plugin.dataaccess.aspects  
    de.espirit.firstspirit.client.plugin.report  
    de.espirit.firstspirit.ui.operations  
    de.espirit.firstspirit.webedit.plugin.report
    Provides interfaces and types for web client report plugins.

    This package provides types, interfaces and classes, that are to be used to integrate web client plugins via the public hotspot of FirstSpirit into the reporting area of the web client.
